description: Penny "The Tarrasque" Barber and Izamar "La Diabla" Gutierrez are a pretty close match in terms of weight class and determination, but, let's be honest, someone gets their ass kicked all over the mat and ends up with her legs around her head and a strap-on cock deep in her ass. Who do you think it is?
title: Summer Vengeance Tournament: One Match Closer to Determining the Champ
